{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Destroy_GIF.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><br>Besiege is a physics building game about constructing mechanical machines to annihilate armies, obliterate castles and overcome challenging obstacles. Conquer the campaign or skirmish with friends in Multiplayer!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Build_Machines_of_Mass_Destruction_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Create tanks, planes, helicopters, sports cars, catapults, rockets, giant mechs- anything you can imagine- with Besiege\u2019s intuitive &amp; flexible building system and extensive 70+ block collection!<br><br>The game\u2019s intricate physics system creates a satisfying building &amp; simulation experience, whether you\u2019re the harbinger of destruction or your machine is falling apart.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/1-c650c70ef5.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Conquer_The_Campaign_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Conquer your way through a singleplayer campaign of 55 destructible levels. Spanning across four island nations, each with its own environment, the campaign will pit you against unique civilizations ripe for conquest.<br><br>Cruise through Besiege\u2019s huge sandbox levels, terrorizing their inhabitants, honing your craft &amp; testing your ingenious prototypes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Discover_Community_Made_Machines_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Unlock more than 200,000 community made machines via the Steam Workshop, all available to download &amp; play in your own game!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/dinorex001.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Play_With_Friends_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Besiege Multiverse is a portal for you to connect with other players and unleash chaos in multiplayer. Go head-to-head in epic machine combat or compete against your friends to complete level objectives and win custom game modes. Work cooperatively to conquer levels, complete puzzles and lay waste to armies &amp; fortresses.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Multiverse001a.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Create_Custom_Levels_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Besiege\u2019s powerful level editing tools will enable you to wage war with AI armies and build custom environments with your friends! Make changes to levels in real time and create unique multiplayer experiences with the editor\u2019s logic system. Robot wars, motor racing, football; there\u2019s no end to the creative possibilities!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/leveleditor001.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_A_Decade_of_Mods_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Besiege has built in support which has enabled our community to produce hundreds of mods and thousands of custom levels &amp; skin packs. Easy to find and simple to install with Besiege\u2019s Steam Workshop integration &amp; our in-game modloader.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/HUDmod001.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><br>With more than 20,000 members, you\u2019ll be sure to find help building, modding, skinning and if you\u2019re looking for a challenge you can take part in one of the building contests.<br>The community Discord is also a great place to find other people to play multiplayer games with!<br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A Swift Siege","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/f8f30542db3abca590c508f14f518020d48ba8c9.jpg"},{"name":"The Handyman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/71acd25348ecc86ae0f5e3fef1b39f0a3e28af60.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta Go Fast","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/b6db1d8176b402a9f9ffbdd1040b02c945f4afc3.jpg"},{"name":"A Whole New World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/d143f7ba3bdac36b13ddb2c72f00b10650d613f5.jpg"},{"name":"Sharing is caring","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/92896687f73e1307c53bb867ffbb6e2c0bc8291e.jpg"},{"name":"The copy-cat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/c6164712596afd1600b34134daa8332021142e69.jpg"},{"name":"Thunderstruck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/d223e88208f3616e8a936d4c6e88e89fd7364252.jpg"},{"name":"All Under Control","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/fc90eb2b006f1dde5decb27b1e0bf28b2f0d0f1a.jpg"},{"name":"Carnage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/cabf669af5b4da50646f6ff0ddfb39f6598ec1b5.jpg"},{"name":"Pyromaniac","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/346010/6b52fd8f128eca83cf144934d17729e69e860aad.jpg"}],"total":50},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738346315","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738346315","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/c0baf8adef0b0c7221d0dc1a0ea7672554d6fa21/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738346315","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/c0baf8adef0b0c7221d0dc1a0ea7672554d6fa21/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738346315","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17},{"description":"Remote Play on Tablet","id":42},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>New Expansion Available!</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Special_announcement_section_DLC_Buy_now_616x200.png?t=1738346315\" /></p><br><h1>Just Updated</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_New_Expanded_Campaign_616x291_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Destroy_GIF.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><br>Besiege is a physics building game about constructing mechanical machines to annihilate armies, obliterate castles and overcome challenging obstacles. Conquer the campaign or skirmish with friends in Multiplayer!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Build_Machines_of_Mass_Destruction_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Create tanks, planes, helicopters, sports cars, catapults, rockets, giant mechs- anything you can imagine- with Besiege\u2019s intuitive &amp; flexible building system and extensive 70+ block collection!<br><br>The game\u2019s intricate physics system creates a satisfying building &amp; simulation experience, whether you\u2019re the harbinger of destruction or your machine is falling apart.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/1-c650c70ef5.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Conquer_The_Campaign_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Conquer your way through a singleplayer campaign of 55 destructible levels. Spanning across four island nations, each with its own environment, the campaign will pit you against unique civilizations ripe for conquest.<br><br>Cruise through Besiege\u2019s huge sandbox levels, terrorizing their inhabitants, honing your craft &amp; testing your ingenious prototypes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Discover_Community_Made_Machines_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Unlock more than 200,000 community made machines via the Steam Workshop, all available to download &amp; play in your own game!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/dinorex001.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Play_With_Friends_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Besiege Multiverse is a portal for you to connect with other players and unleash chaos in multiplayer. Go head-to-head in epic machine combat or compete against your friends to complete level objectives and win custom game modes. Work cooperatively to conquer levels, complete puzzles and lay waste to armies &amp; fortresses.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Multiverse001a.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_Create_Custom_Levels_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Besiege\u2019s powerful level editing tools will enable you to wage war with AI armies and build custom environments with your friends! Make changes to levels in real time and create unique multiplayer experiences with the editor\u2019s logic system. Robot wars, motor racing, football; there\u2019s no end to the creative possibilities!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/leveleditor001.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/Besiege_A_Decade_of_Mods_ENG.png?t=1738346315\" /><br>Besiege has built in support which has enabled our community to produce hundreds of mods and thousands of custom levels &amp; skin packs. Easy to find and simple to install with Besiege\u2019s Steam Workshop integration &amp; our in-game modloader.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/346010/extras/HUDmod001.gif?t=1738346315\" /><br><br>With more than 20,000 members, you\u2019ll be sure to find help building, modding, skinning and if you\u2019re looking for a challenge you can take part in one of the building contests.<br>The community Discord is also a great place to find other people to play multiplayer games with!<br>","developers":["Spiderling Studios"],"dlc":[2165710,2959930,2959970],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","i